<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>diǎn rán diǎn rán 迦南117</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 diǎn rán diǎn rán fú yīn de huǒ, chuī qǐ chuī qǐ fú yīn hào jiǎo,
 héng dù zhǎng jiāng, kuà yuè huáng hé, zǒu xiàng cǎo yuán, zǒu xiàng shā mò.
 fú yīn de yǒng shì men, bēn pǎo zài huán xíng dào shàng,
 bù pà kù shǔ, bù pà yán hán, yào zǒu biàn měi yī gè de fāng.
 cóng rì chū zhī de, dào rì luò zhī chù,
 yǒu nǐ hāi hāi, yǒu wǒ hāi hāi, wèi zhǔ zhēng zhàn de shēn yǐng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>117</hymn_number>
</song>